Utterance.UttText: In bed 6 is Tom MacCay, 46 yrs old, under Dr Saldy.
He came in with pain and difficulty of breathing for a week and he also have a lung cyst for 5 yrs now but was assymptomatic before.
He is a new admission and he just came in.
He is on oxygen 3l/nasal prongs, self caring and ambulant and normal diet.
